Path: godot/classes/class_navigationserver2d.rst
Summary: An overview of the NavigationServer2D singleton, its purpose as the main interface for 2D navigation, and how to access it.

Inherits: Object

Server interface for 2D navigation.

NavigationServer2D is the server responsible for all 2D navigation. It can create multiple navigation maps which are made of navigation polygons. These polygons can be connected by links. The server is not meant to be used directly but is used by nodes like NavigationRegion2D and TileMap. To use the server's functions, you must get the singleton instance.
